                        <br />
                        <h2 style="margin:0 ;">
                            Looking for a <br />
                            <b style="color:#AECB91">perfect</b>  place to <br />
                            plan your own <br />
                            <b style="color:#AECB91">social events ?</b> <br /><br />
                        </h2>

                        <a href="/POIs" class="btn-get-started scrollto " style="background-color: #31943b;">Explore places here</a>
                        <br /><br /><br />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="container" style="font-family: sans-serif;margin:0% -10%  ;text-align:right;color: #fff;font-weight: bold;background-size: cover;">
                        <br />
                        <h2 style="margin:0 ;">
                            <b>1 in 4</b><br />
                            Elders experiences <br />
                            high level of social <br />
                            interaction anxiety <br /><br />
                        </h2>

                        <a href="/Home/About/" class="btn-get-started scrollto " style="background-color: #31943b;">Other Facts</a>
                        <br /><br /><br />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
