            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="row" hidden>
            <div class="col-lg-6 pt-6 pt-lg-0 order-1 order-lg-1 d-flex align-items-center">
                <div data-aos="zoom-out">
                    <h1 style="font-family: sans-serif;margin-top:30px;text-align: left;color: #fff;font-weight: bold;font-size: 4em;background-size: cover;text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #404040;"><span>Caring Square</span></h1>
                    <h2 style="font-family: sans-serif;margin-top:30px;text-align:justify;color: #fff;font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.5em;background-size: cover;text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #404040;">Let's fight loneliness together! A day spent with your friends or elderly family members is a day well spent. A helper application to plan your day is just a few clicks away. <br /><br /></h2>
                    <div class="">
                        <br />
                        <a href="/Account/Login" class="btn-get-started scrollto " style="background-color: #31943b;margin-top:63px;">Get Started</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 hero-img order-lg-2 text-center" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-delay="300">
                <h2 style="font-family: sans-serif;margin-top:30px;text-align: center;color: #fff;font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.8em;background-size: cover;text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #404040;"> <span>DID YOU KNOW?</span></h2>
                <div class="box aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100" style="margin-top: 30px">

                    <a href="/Home/About">
                        <img src="../img/OneinFour.png" alt="" style="width:50%; height:60% ; text-align:right;">
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="">
                    <br />
                    <a href="/Home/About" class="btn-get-started scrollto " style="background-color: #31943b;margin-top:-6px;">Click Here to Know More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <svg class="hero-waves" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 24 150 28 " preserveAspectRatio="none">
